        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_mamba.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository ba047c5b-fb6e-48ec-a893-6717c3e36f5b).Image",
        "Description": "Good day comrade. Your targets are Marta Clerici and Cristina Dionisi. Clerici&apos;s real name is Janet Green and she works for the NSA. She is currently undercover in Sapienza to exchange information with Dionisi who used to work for us as a spy through her music career but now decided to defect. She has valuable information and the Kreml wants both of them killed in a public way that does not fall back on us. So this mission should look like a terror act and thus some casualties are allowed.",
